        includes indieauth and a micropub endpoint
        
        Documentation
        -------------
        
        The full documentation is at https://django-indieweb.readthedocs.org.
        
        Quickstart
        ----------
        
        Install django-indieweb::
        
            pip install django-indieweb
        
        Then use it in a project::
        
            import indieweb
        
