        History
        -------
        
        0.0.5 (2019-05-19)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * Auth endpoint works with https://pin13.net/login/ \o/
        * Use black for code formatting
        * Better package infrastructure
        * Require python >= 3.6
        
        0.0.4 (2016-06-14)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * exempt csrf checking
        
        0.0.3 (2016-06-13)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * added migrations
        
        0.0.2 (2016-05-15)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * Auth and Token endpoints with some tests.
        
        0.0.1 (2016-05-14)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * First release on PyPI.
        
